Often we need to bulk assign issues to either the reporter or the project lead - for example when a team member leaves, all their issues need reassigning.  For project lead this has to be done per project, and for reporter, per issue.  Needless to say, this is time consuming.  

This would be much quicker if the bulk assign operation had options to automatically assign to the project lead or reporter.  This would ideally work across multiple projects.

This would also be useful for individual issues via the Operations menu in the left-hand navigation bar.

